// Datasheet for `vstore`: it requires the components `a`/`b` and storage for the `Cell` shape. A
// datasheet describes requirements only — it lists the component types the driver must provide and a
// storage requirement (`Cell[4]`, the minimum), but never defines the `Cell` shape itself (the driver
// does that). Support file.
// RUN: true
a :: float;
b :: float;
[4] Cell;
